                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote><!--Arena--><p>Arena notes that the quadrangular module of the individual letters is regular, letters with neat terminal serifs, elegantly cut, comparable in size and form to the other surviving fragments of the cadastral inscription, ISic001174.</p>
